</p>
<p class="para">“Hey, Nii-sama”</p>
<p class="para">Furiae suddenly stopped walking.</p>
<p class="para">“Let’s stop being royalty—starting today.”</p>
<p class="para">Now she says that…</p>
<p class="para">“As long as we’re royal, people will keep trying to use us, to kill us.
