<p class="para">Caim froze where he stood.</p>
<p class="para">Furiae was lying on the floor.
    <br>Her body was wrapped in a spiral of white light.
</p>
<p class="para">“Furiae!”</p>
<p class="para">He rushed to her and lifted her into his arms. Her body radiated a strange heat.
